.container
  .row
    .col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
      %hr
  .row
    .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.center
      =image_tag ('speakeasy.png'),  style: 'width:100%;height:auto;max-width: 400px'
    .col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
      %h1.h1custom1
        The Speakeasy!
        %p
          %i (10 max)
      %p
        From one of the creators of Project Escape, experience "Escape Room Horsham's" newest room, The Speakeasy!
      %p
        Leveraging the newest escape room technology and the BEST visuals and scenic production in the area, you take on the role
        of government agents, tasked with taking down the criminal mob boss Maxi Malone.
      %p
        Go back in time to the 1920's and under cover as bar employees to find his hidden ledger book
        which will help put Maxi behind bars.
      %p
        %b This room is brought to you by Escape Room Horsham, and is NOT part of Project Escape in Conshohocken.
        %b Visit this location at 149 Gibraltar Rd, Horsham, Pa, 19044.

        %b You can find more information about Escape Room Horsham at their facebook page:
        %br
        %br
        = link_to "http://facebook.com/escaperoomhorsham" do
          =image_tag ('Facebook_logo.png'), style: 'width:100%;height:auto;max-width: 40px'
          Escape Room Horsham
      %br
  .row
    .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.center
      =image_tag ('nuke-logo-wide.png'),  style: 'width:100%;height:auto;max-width: 400px'
    .col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
      %h1.h1custom1
        The Meltdown!
        %p
          %i (min 3 players | 8 max)
      %p
        Prevent the nuclear meltdown in Project Escape's newest room!
      %p
        You are new employees and your first day is not going to go as planned!
      %p
        A disaster occurs and it's going to be up to you and your team to stop the Nuclear Meltdown and save the city!
      =render 'layouts/bookings'
      %br
      %br
      %br
  .row
    .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.center
      =image_tag ('heist-banner.png'),  style: 'width:100%;height:auto;max-width: 400px'
    .col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
      %h1.h1custom1
        The Big Score
        %p
          %i The Heist of the Century (min 4 players | 10 max)
      %p
        %b
          An
          %span.yellow instant classic!
          This is the perfect room for new escape room goers!
          Offering a
          %span.yellow moderate difficulty
          level, by the time you are done, you'll be an escape room
          vet, and ready for our next, slightly more challenging room!
      %hr
      %p
        You have been recruited by the infamous and renowned
        theft ring, the
        %strong Shrouded Hand,
        and tasked with stealing one of the most famous diamonds in the world,
        the
        %strong Millennium Diamond!
      %p
        The mark? The Viper - one of the head bosses of the Syndicate, a darker, more
        ruthless theft ring.
      %p
        Break in, steal the diamond, then get out!  Be quick though, you only have an hour before
        The Viper and his goons get back!
      %p
        Are you up to the task?
      =render 'layouts/bookings'
  %hr
  .row
    .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.center
      =image_tag ('banner-harrypotter.png'),  style: 'width:100%;height:auto;max-width: 400px'
    .col-lg-8.col-md-8.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
      %h1.h1custom1
        The Wizard's Secret
        %p
          %i (min 3 players | 8 max)
      %p
        Escape from the dreaded Witch and Wizard Prison!
      %p
        You have been tricked by a dark wizard and forced to take his spot in the dreaded prison. Your easiest task will be escaping the cell!
      %p
        Once you're out, you'll encounter a magical world of potions, spells and wizardry!  Can you figure out the Wizard's secret before the guards realize you're gone?!
      =render 'layouts/bookings'